    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3147220/extras/d290ffe8a05dc0c51564a408293ece03.avif?t=1749385135\" width=616 height=72 /></span>见习修女露米娜在圣特里尼娅教的修女培训学校中过着平静的日子。然而有一天，她最好的朋友丽娜被一个神秘组织绑架了。为了拯救她，露米娜不得不使用祖母传下来的技能书，但这背后的代价将无法估量……与此同时，一个新兴的可疑宗教——新利多姆教，开始在小镇上引发种种奇怪的事件，将露米娜和整个小镇逐步吞入诡异的气氛中……</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3147220/extras/cbdeb8b8a6caa3c0dcbcc4015a3b9956.avif?t=1749385135\" width=616 height=73 /></span>无需升级、刷怪或繁琐的战斗！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在这个以故事为主的RPG游戏中，尽情享受修女露米娜的故事吧！跟随露米娜，应对邪教的种种威胁去拯救丽娜！然而，笼罩小镇的阴影中潜藏着许多谜团……露米娜能否顺利克服这次考验？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3147220/extras/e6835bb6e856e1266595589a3d8ef0d4.avif?t=1749385135\" width=616 height=73 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3147220/extras/bb26b72c7863bfdf7f424966abafff03.avif?t=1749385135\" width=616 height=275 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3147220/extras/d4161ca60f0ca7983691c696d1a7783b.avif?t=1749385135\" width=616 height=73 /></span><strong>丰富的内容</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >从祈祷、布施到忏悔室，多种不同情境和场景供你体验！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>多重结局</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏有两个全然不同的结局，根据你的选择来决定游戏走向！露米娜是会走上黑暗的道路，还是会忠于自己的信仰？决定权掌握在你手中！</p>",
